2005-09-13  Miloslav Trmac  <mitr@redhat.com>

	* configure.in: Version 0.54.
	* Makefile.am (lib_libuser_la_LDFLAGS): Update revision.

	* NEWS: Update.

	* apps/apputil.h
	* lib/internal.h: Add G_GNUC_INTERNAL to all declarations.

