2004-11-08  Miloslav Trmac  <mitr@redhat.com>

	* lib/user.c (lu_default_int): Use id_t.

	* lib/user.c (lu_get_first_unused_id): Change the interface to use
	id_t.  Don't allow (id_t)-1.
	* lib/user_private.h: Update prototype.

